
# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [0.1.3] - 2024-01-27

### Changed
    Added a function to get component using the Identifier

## [0.1.2] - 2024-01-27

### Changed
    Changed lifetime trait function to non-reference

## [0.1.1] - 2024-01-27

### Added
    Added a lifetime feature
    - Added a BioglocalTrait for lifetime specification
    - Added a system to act as a garbage collector

## [0.1.0] - 2024-01-27

### Added
    Released first version of bevy_family
    - Allow easy creation, updating, and removal of parent-child components with events
    - Using resource to keep track of history of events